**Problem 3: Check if a Number is a Power of Two**

This problem involves checking if a given number is a power of two.

### C++ Solution
```cpp
#include <iostream>

bool isPowerOfTwo(int n) {
    if (n <= 0) {
        return false;
    }
    return (n & (n - 1)) == 0;
}

int main() {
    int n;
    std::cout << "Enter a number: ";
    std::cin >> n;
    if (isPowerOfTwo(n)) {
        std::cout << n << " is a power of two." << std::endl;
    } else {
        std::cout << n << " is not a power of two." << std::endl;
    }
    return 0;
}
